    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🟥 地狱方块</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到地狱。忘掉但丁的九层圆环吧——这里一切都是方的、机械的、荒谬得离谱。<br>这就是 <i>地狱方块</i> ——谜题房间，每一关都有一个罪人、一个恶魔，还有一些根本不讲逻辑但偏偏能动的奇怪机关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/d055300eeaa0ed9cab68defa04c5ae8b.poster.avif?t=1772274347\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/d055300eeaa0ed9cab68defa04c5ae8b.webm?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/d055300eeaa0ed9cab68defa04c5ae8b.mp4?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👼 第一关你要救一个摇滚天使，长着豆娘翅膀。对，他一边弹吉他riff，一边冷嘲热讽，看着你的脑子烧得比第一个罪人的香烟还快。<br>🚬 罪人1：抽烟太多，把全家和狗都熏成了腊肉。现在他不停地跳，想够到那根巨型香烟。解决谜题，骗过恶魔，让他吸上一口。烟雾腾起，打开通往下一个方块的大门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ddfc4206526e47bbb275908ea8eaead4.poster.avif?t=1772274347\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ddfc4206526e47bbb275908ea8eaead4.webm?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ddfc4206526e47bbb275908ea8eaead4.mp4?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗 罪人2：开车时总喜欢溅行人一身水。现在他像西西弗斯一样推着车上坡，只为看它再滚下去。你的任务：用咖啡哄睡恶魔，修好汽车，一起开到下一关。<br>🔊 罪人3：音响狂魔，音量大到把邻居都吓跑。现在他在巨型音箱上蹦迪，直到能躺进悬空的床。你需要用机械手臂把他塞进去……然后让天花板塌下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如此往复——每一关更荒唐，每一个罪更愚蠢，每一种惩罚更变态。坐上地狱游乐设施，操控六脚机器人小卖部，抓恶魔进机械陷阱，最后炸飞整关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ce1eead9fe672d198899c5ad08a47503.poster.avif?t=1772274347\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ce1eead9fe672d198899c5ad08a47503.webm?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/ce1eead9fe672d198899c5ad08a47503.mp4?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙ <strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😈 荒谬的罪，荒谬到家的惩罚。<br>🧩 谜题让你一边思考，一边爆笑，一边破口大骂。<br>🎸 冷嘲热讽的摇滚天使当向导。<br>🚬 烟、咖啡、噪音、垃圾袋，还有地狱机械学。<br>🔥 穿越地狱方块之旅：从烟雾迷宫到岩浆桥梁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/8bba32a1d026ce45f025ff212d10ac7c.poster.avif?t=1772274347\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/8bba32a1d026ce45f025ff212d10ac7c.webm?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/8bba32a1d026ce45f025ff212d10ac7c.mp4?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>地狱方块</i> 是一款献给厌倦“圣光与美德”游戏的玩家的黑色解谜。<br>在这里，你帮罪人满足小小恶习，智斗恶魔，一路下坠深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到逻辑-方块化的地狱。能活下来的不是聪明人，而是最愤世嫉俗的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/5493f767d75a9e182525876e59838448.poster.avif?t=1772274347\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/5493f767d75a9e182525876e59838448.webm?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005260/extras/5493f767d75a9e182525876e59838448.mp4?t=1772274347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
